<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Johann III. von Hohenzollern, Burggraf von Nürnberg</head><p>Der Rat kündigt einen Gesandten wegen Otto Heyden, Bürger zu Nürnberg, an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_522" id="260v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_522_r1l1">Burggraf Johanſen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_522_r1l2"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Als vns ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> <expan>geſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat von Otten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_522_r1l3">Heydens wegen / das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir wol vernomen / laſſen vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_522_r1l4">gnade wiſſen / daʒ vvir vnſerſelbs botſchaft <expan>kürcʒlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_522_r1l5"><expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſach vvegen cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> ſchıcken <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> / müntlıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_522_r1l6">mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden dauon cʒureden / vnd wo vvir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> lieb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_522_r1l7">vnd dinſte beweiſen <expan>möchte<ex>n</ex></expan> / des <expan>w<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vvir wıllig vnd teten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_522_r1l8">das <expan>allcʒ<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ıııj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Mıchael<ex>is</ex></expan> Anno xij<hi rend="sup">o</hi> / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_522" id="260v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Burggraf Johansen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat von Otten Heydens wegen, das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol vernomen; lassen wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade wissen, daz wir unserselbs
                        botschaft <expan>kürczlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von
                            <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sach wegen czu
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> schicken <expan>wölle<ex>n,</ex></expan>
                        müntlich mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden davon czu reden; und wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> lieb und dinste beweisen
                                <expan>möchte<ex>n</ex></expan>, des <expan>w<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        wir willig und teten das <expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iiii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Michael<ex>is</ex></expan> anno xii<hi rend="sup">o</hi>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
